tting against a stock and then publishing=C2=A0falsehoods about the company=
 to drive down the stock is classic fraud, and no one will be sympathetic i=
f you say you made an honest mistake.=C2=A0Even if you publish stuff that i=
s=C2=A0right, people will be suspicious. There is an ongoing US Department =
of Justice  investigation of activist short sellers, =E2=80=9Cprobing possi=
ble coordination surrounding the publication of short reports, looking for =
signs of market manipulation or other trading abuses.=E2=80=9D Is Hunterbro=
